			<article id="post-1205" class="post-1205 post type-post hentry category-life">
			<header>
				<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=1205" title="Permalink to Hang by a Thread Not a Rope" rel="bookmark">Hang by a Thread Not a Rope</a></h2>
							</header>
				<div class="entry-summary">
				<p>I can&#8217;t do the sight of it justice. The bright golden, orange leaves of this maple tree, five stories high. Every day, I&#8217;ve watched it change. It stayed green as the weed-tree behind it turned yellow and lost all its &hellip; <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=1205">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
			</div><!-- .entry-summary -->
	
			<div class="entry-utility">
								<div class="entry-meta">
					<span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?author=87" title="View all posts by LoriC">LoriC</a></span> <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=1205" title="4:37 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">November 7, 2013</span></a>				</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
													<span class="cat-links">
						<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Life" rel="category">Life</a>					</span>
					<span class="meta-sep">|</span>
												<span class="comments-link"><span>Comments Off</span></span>
			</div><!-- .entry-utility -->
		</article><!-- #post-## -->

		
	

			<article id="post-1190" class="post-1190 post type-post hentry category-life">
			<header>
				<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=1190" title="Permalink to The Experience of All That" rel="bookmark">The Experience of All That</a></h2>
							</header>
				<div class="entry-summary">
				<p>Woke up thinking that I hadn&#8217;t gotten the Sequoias right. In my book. The description wasn&#8217;t quite accurate, felt shallow. Then I remembered there are no Sequoias in my book. It was from a dream. I felt a moment of &hellip; <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=1190">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
			</div><!-- .entry-summary -->
	
			<div class="entry-utility">
								<div class="entry-meta">
					<span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?author=87" title="View all posts by LoriC">LoriC</a></span> <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=1190" title="5:10 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">September 20, 2013</span></a>				</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
													<span class="cat-links">
						<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Life" rel="category">Life</a>					</span>
					<span class="meta-sep">|</span>
												<span class="comments-link"><span>Comments Off</span></span>
			</div><!-- .entry-utility -->
		</article><!-- #post-## -->

		
	

			<article id="post-1173" class="post-1173 post type-post hentry category-life">
			<header>
				<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=1173" title="Permalink to A Full Life" rel="bookmark">A Full Life</a></h2>
							</header>
				<div class="entry-summary">
				<p>What does it mean to have a full life? My perspective shifts all around on this, determined by my very changeable moods. But by whatever definition, this week my life was full. It was so good that when I reflect &hellip; <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=1173">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
			</div><!-- .entry-summary -->
	
			<div class="entry-utility">
								<div class="entry-meta">
					<span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?author=87" title="View all posts by LoriC">LoriC</a></span> <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?p=1173" title="9:12 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">August 30, 2013</span></a>				</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
													<span class="cat-links">
						<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140902043315/http://lifeandmusic.loricarson.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Life" rel="category">Life</a>					</span>
